    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  men with type 1 diabetes (WHO criteria)

          -  age 35-50 years

          -  duration of diabetes &gt; 10 years

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  P-creatinine&gt; 120 micromol/l

          -  other acute or chronic disease, or type of treatment that makes the patient unsuitable
             to participate, valuated by the investigator

          -  non intact skin on the measuring spots

          -  the patient is unable to understand the informed consent
      </textblock>
    </criteria>
